author: Steven Ruiz
title: Last-place fantasy football owner recreates Cassie’s ‘Me & U’ video with amazing results | For The Win
text:
By: Steven Ruiz | February 21, 2017 2:33 pm Follow @theStevenRuiz 
There’s nothing worse than finishing in last place in your fantasy football league, especially if your league happens to have a last-place punishment, as this unfortunate Michigan State student learned. 
After finishing in last place in his league, he had to recreate the music video for Cassie’s 2006 hit “Me & U,” and we have to say he did a fantastic job. 
If you had trouble figuring it out, Cassie’s version is the on the left. Just wanted to clear that up, because it can be difficult to tell these two videos apart. 
Nailed it.
